## KPI classification logic

Providers are categorized each evaluation period (weekly) based on KPI thresholds derived from the performance bands above.  
These labels are used by downstream automation to trigger alerts, summaries, and provider outreach workflows.

### Classification categories

| Category | Description |
|---|---|
| **TOP PERFORMER** | Consistently exceeds performance expectations |
| **WATCH** | Metrics are within acceptable range but trending negatively |
| **NEEDS INTERVENTION** | Performance falls below acceptable thresholds and requires ops follow-up |

---

### KPI thresholds (weekly evaluation)

A provider is classified using the following rules:

#### ğŸŸ¢ TOP PERFORMER
